NewsfeedEntryType Data Type

The type of newsfeed entry.

Values
value description
CREATE The object was created.
STATUS_CHANGE The status of the object changed.
ASSIGNED The object was assigned to someone new.
REMOVED The object was removed.
MEMBERS_REMOVED The object had members removed.
MEMBERS_ADDED The object had members added.
MEMBERS_SET The members list was set.
MEMBERS_UNSET The members list was unset.
MODIFY The object was modified.
COMMENT_ADDED A comment was added to the object.
COMMENT_REMOVED A comment was removed from the object.
COMMENT_MODIFIED A comment was modified.
ATTACHMENT_ADDED An attachment was added to the object.
ATTACHMENT_REMOVED An attachment was removed from the object.
SYSTEM_TASK_SUMMARY The system task summary was updated. This happens when the system automatically changes the task list because of rules.
IMPORTED Internal use only.
PHASE_CHANGE The incident's phase changed.
ROW_ADDED A row was added to a datatable
ROW_MODIFIED A row was modified to a datatable
ROW_DELETED A row was deleted to a datatable
ATTACHMENT_MOVED An attachment was moved from one parent to another parent.
